org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.optimizer.calcite.cost

Class HiveCost

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.optimizer.calcite.cost.HiveCost
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.calcite.plan.RelOptCost

    public class HiveCost
extends Object
implements org.apache.calcite.plan.RelOptCost
    NOTE:
    1. Hivecost normalizes cpu and io in to time.
    2. CPU, IO cost is added together to find the query latency.
    3. If query latency is equal then row count is compared.
